air:Brand.Name: Economy Basic
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Basic
BASIC
air:Brand.air:Text:
Your ECONOMY BASIC fare with KLM is ideal for those travelling light and includes:
• Online check in. • Ergonomically designed seating with even more comfort options available. • Complimentary snacks and drinks on board. • Check in a bag for an additional fee. • Carry on one bag + one other small item, combined max weight 12kg. • Earn 25% Flying Blue Miles. • Rebook for an additional fee. • Cancellation not permitted.
If the flight will be operated by another airline then the onboard product or service might be different.
